    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                 <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/0ec7e8c2e2d839dc4aa39b7bf7239be8.avif?t=1764627450\" width=542 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A curious little girl finds herself lost in an <strong>unknown world.</strong> Looking for answers and trying to understand what is going on, and deal with her own emotions as well. Lyara begins her journey in this new world, making new friendships along the way, and facing numerous challenges forcing her to grow up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join this adventure to surpass challenges and learn with the kid.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/51e6ba65eed49e1a7932dfc850f3e783.poster.avif?t=1764627450\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/51e6ba65eed49e1a7932dfc850f3e783.webm?t=1764627450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/51e6ba65eed49e1a7932dfc850f3e783.mp4?t=1764627450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/c9ee4acd527e8dfd9480fb9f194bc328.avif?t=1764627450\" width=542 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lyara is a <strong>challenging 2D platform game</strong>   including multiple mechanics according to the world, demanding player's agility and precision, as well as puzzle resolution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You will find a great challenge in this crazy adventure!</strong> Like the classics platform games,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Lyara will make the player experience a rich narrative with fun and enjoyable moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/092dd44b4fd678a99cb5ff7a9410aad5.poster.avif?t=1764627450\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/092dd44b4fd678a99cb5ff7a9410aad5.webm?t=1764627450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/092dd44b4fd678a99cb5ff7a9410aad5.mp4?t=1764627450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/7ede25b60a8e73897b5f04a37a382cbd.avif?t=1764627450\" width=542 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New enviroments and mechanics each world demands new player's skills. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You wont rest until every inch of this universe is explored!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/58c45a8fa06549f5d81ad626a1706b0b.poster.avif?t=1764627450\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/58c45a8fa06549f5d81ad626a1706b0b.webm?t=1764627450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/f978e8b515eba73424af6afa3715171d.avif?t=1764627450\" width=542 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover <strong>multiple worlds</strong> with unique characteristics that will develop the character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/e76743c2ecfa402aaee3d7f3e56415f5.avif?t=1764627450\" width=616 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/9e5eaa3993a511c7bfb9ab248ae11328.avif?t=1764627450\" width=616 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During this journey, find out more about Lyara`s past, search for answers and meet new characters that will help you understand more about this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every new friendship along the way make part of protagonist's life in a different way, helping her to grow up. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/53b640ce8150eb809748ec94a5872ce9.webp?t=1764627450\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871260/extras/53b640ce8150eb809748ec94a5872ce9.poster.avif?t=1764627450\" class=\"bb_img\" width=350 height=234 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And more!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original Soundtrack</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore this great universe with an original soundtrack that will be with you along the way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collectables</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Look for collectables during the adventure that will tell more about the story and level up the challenge!</p>",
